com.vmware.nsx.logical_routers.routing

Class RoutingFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.logical_routers.routing.RoutingFactory

  • public class RoutingFactory
extends Object
    RoutingFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx.logical_routers.routing package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
